      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, just getting the audit results back for the Q3 peer-review cycle. There's been some heated feedback from the DEI committee regarding the \"SciValidator\" selection patterns—specifically how much higher the acceptance rates are for Western Ivy League institutions versus researchers from the Global South. Can you explain the logic behind these metrics?",
